"%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22content%22%20id%3D%22page_team%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Cdiv%20style%3D%22width%3A%20100%25%3B%20text-align%3A%20center%3B%22%3E%3Cimg%20class%3D%22std%20circle%22%20src%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fupdate.lanterlite.com%2Fassets%2Fwww.lanterlite.com%2Fimg%2Fpage_team%2Fmembers%2Fifandhanip.webp%22%20style%3D%22width%3A%2025%25%3B%20border-radius%3A%2050%25%3B%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22title%20theme%20fttl%22%3EIfan%20Dhani%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22subtitle%20theme%20fsttl%22%3EFounder%20and%20CEO%20Lanterlite%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EBismillah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EIfan%20Dhani%20Prasojo%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Lanterlite.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EIn%202012%2C%20Ifan%2C%20who%20was%20still%20in%20high%20school%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20the%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20company%20that%20is%20engaged%20in%20improving%20the%20welfare%20of%20Muslims.%20This%20desire%20arose%20from%20his%20concern%20at%20seeing%20oppressed%20Muslims%20in%20Palestine.%20So%20that%20encouraged%20him%20to%20make%20a%20community%20called%20'Seribu%20Lentera'.%20Then%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20used%20this%20name%20as%20a%20means%20for%20preaching%20and%20motivating%20people%20through%20social%20medias%20and%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EIn%202015%2C%20Ifan%2C%20who%20had%20entered%20second%20grade%20at%20the%20Bandung%20State%20Polytechnic%20(Polban)%2C%20began%20studying%20Islam%20through%20his%20indirect%20teacher%2C%20Ustaz%20Khalid%20Basalamah%2C%20whom%20he%20met%20through%20the%20internet.%20Until%20at%20one%20point%2C%20he%20felt%20there%20was%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20system%20he%20used%20in%20Seribu%20Lentera%20with%20Islamic%20law%20that%20he%20had%20learned%20at%20that%20time.%20So%20in%202016%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20dismiss%20Seribu%20Lentera%20and%20make%20a%20new%20community%20called%20'Lanterlite'%20with%20a%20new%20system..%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%20%20%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3ESince%20then%2C%20he%20began%20developing%20Lanterlite%20by%20himself.%20Ifan%2C%20who%20at%20that%20time%20entered%20Informatics%20faculty%2C%20made%20him%20recognize%20and%20study%20programming%20science%20in%20his%20campus%2C%20so%20he%20could%20develop%20the%20first%20mobile%20application%20called%20%22Al-Khulafa%20Ar-Rasyidun%20Encyclopedia%3A%20ID%22%2C%20an%20application%20that%20contains%20the%20history%20of%20the%20first%20four%20leaders%20in%20Islam%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20(peace%20be%20upon%20him)%20which%20originated%20from%20the%20Book%20of%20%3Ci%3EAl-Bidayah%20wan%20Nihayah%3C%2Fi%3E%20by%20Imam%20Ibn%20Kathir.%20Then%2C%20he%20published%20the%20application%20on%20February%2010%2C%202017%2C%20which%20he%20made%20as%20the%20date%20of%20the%20establishment%20of%20Lanterlite..%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EIn%20mid%202017%2C%20Ifan%20faced%20obstacles%20in%20developing%20Lanterlite%20due%20to%20his%20busy%20life%20in%20college.%20This%20was%20%20continued%20until%20his%20graduation%20in%20mid-2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22theme%20fp%22%3EAfter%20his%20graduation%20in%20August%202018%2C%20Ifan%20back%20to%20develop%20Lanterlite%20more%20freely%20so%20that%20in%20December%202018%20to%20January%202019%2C%20Ifan%20successfully%20publishes%20two%20mobile%20applications%2C%20Qulite%20(digital%20Qur'an)%20and%20Enlite%20(Islamic%20content%20search%20engine).%20At%20its%20peak%2C%20on%20February%203%2C%202019%2C%20he%20announced%20the%20start%20operation%20of%20www.lanterlite.com%20to%20the%20public%20and%20made%20him%20CEO%20and%20founder%20at%20Lanterlite%20until%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E"